window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Safety is an illusion. Security is only a fleeting sense. Peace is a myth. </b></p> <p>Steve and the other survivors in the UK have rebuilt and healed after the brutal end to the reign of Richards. But removing a dictator was only the beginning....</p> <p>Years after a mistake of compassion and humanity, an enemy thought long gone returns to bring down a rain of violence and terror the likes of which they have never seen before.&nbsp;</p> <p>Their society, a peaceful one of trade and cooperation, has moved on from the bloody aftermath of the collapse, but that evolution blunts their teeth to be able to combat the new threat.&nbsp;</p> <p>The call to return to the rainy shores of England is strong for Dan and his fearless accomplices, so they return home to do what they do best: bring justice to a lawless world.</p>"; 
